    "The main observation is that MLFS provides accurate, smaller encoder models at 1/4 the size of the teacher and 1/3 its runtime latency on a single GPU.Ablation Study on Gradient Scaling In supernet training, the weights of maxnet and subnets are shared and trained simultaneously.",
